  "detailed_description": "Dry Body broke free and it was up to Capytu, a powerful and adorable clumsy magical girl, to arrest him and stop him from doing any harm to animals.<br>But fear nothing! She created a bunch of magic blocks so Corpse Seco would stay away from the animals.<br><br>All right, isn't it?<br>...<br><br>Unfortunately not. Because now everyone is trapped in their magic blocks.<br>Now she needs to solve this mess, facing the mysterious figures of Brazilian Folklore, while saving the animals of the Cerrado.<br><br>She accompanies Capytu, the Magical Capybara Girl on her adventure to stop this villain!<br>Solve puzzles, creatively fire your spirits to avoid obstacles and enemies, explore every corner of the maps for unique collectibles, and defeat fearsome creatures from Brazilian regional myths in this unique adventure!<br><br>                                                             <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058100/extras/c439d61b961baec0fadad5c82e3b7e65.poster.avif?t=1715719664\" width=288 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058100/extras/c439d61b961baec0fadad5c82e3b7e65.webm?t=1715719664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <br><br>24 complete levels.<br>Different approaches to platform challenges.<br>Bosses and enemies based on Brazilian regional myths.<br>Capybaras, several of them!!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058100/extras/6aeaa72ddf7d9d1a271cca37de4472c4.apng?t=1715719664\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058100/extras/6aeaa72ddf7d9d1a271cca37de4472c4.poster.avif?t=1715719664\" class=\"bb_img\" width=54 height=54 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058100/extras/2543e714732e17cd3c314c21a78ce8dc.apng?t=1715719664\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058100/extras/2543e714732e17cd3c314c21a78ce8dc.poster.avif?t=1715719664\" class=\"bb_img\" width=54 height=54 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058100/extras/3088fc6ca8df05e23d8a1a3f84b471ee.apng?t=1715719664\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058100/extras/3088fc6ca8df05e23d8a1a3f84b471ee.poster.avif?t=1715719664\" class=\"bb_img\" width=54 height=54 /></picture></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Dry Body broke free and it was up to Capytu, a powerful and adorable clumsy magical girl, to arrest him and stop him from doing any harm to animals.<br>But fear nothing! She created a bunch of magic blocks so Corpse Seco would stay away from the animals.<br><br>All right, isn't it?<br>...<br><br>Unfortunately not. Because now everyone is trapped in their magic blocks.<br>Now she needs to solve this mess, facing the mysterious figures of Brazilian Folklore, while saving the animals of the Cerrado.<br><br>She accompanies Capytu, the Magical Capybara Girl on her adventure to stop this villain!<br>Solve puzzles, creatively fire your spirits to avoid obstacles and enemies, explore every corner of the maps for unique collectibles, and defeat fearsome creatures from Brazilian regional myths in this unique adventure!<br><br>                                                             <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058100/extras/c439d61b961baec0fadad5c82e3b7e65.poster.avif?t=1715719664\" width=288 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058100/extras/c439d61b961baec0fadad5c82e3b7e65.webm?t=1715719664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> <br><br>24 complete levels.<br>Different approaches to platform challenges.<br>Bosses and enemies based on Brazilian regional myths.<br>Capybaras, several of them!!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058100/extras/6aeaa72ddf7d9d1a271cca37de4472c4.apng?t=1715719664\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2058100/extras/6aeaa72ddf7d9d1a271cca37de4472c4.poster.avif?t=1715719664\" class=\"bb_img\" width=54 height=54 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source